<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM8.3">
<l>koṅkumali karuṅkuḻalāḷ kaucalaitaṉ kulamatalāy</l>
<l>taṅkuperum pukaḻccaṉakaṉ ṟirumarukā tācaratī</l>
<l>kaṅkaiyilun tīrttamali kaṇapuratteṉ karumaṇiyē</l>
<l>yeṅkaḷkulat tiṉṉamutē yirākavaṉē tālēlō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You who are the Support of the lineage of Kauśālyā of dark-coloured curls full of fragrance!</l>
<l>O Son of Daśaratha! O sacred Son-in-law of Janaka of great, everlasting fame!</l>
<l>O Apple of my eye from Kaṇapuram rich in [watercourses] purer than the Ganges!</l>
<l>O sweet Nectar of our lineage! O Rāghava! Tālēlō!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
